Package it.essepuntato.earmark.core

Interface Summary
Collection This interface describes collection of collectable items.
EARMARKChildNode  
EARMARKClassURI This interface defines the URI for each EARMARK class.
EARMARKHierarchicalNode  
EARMARKItem This interface defines the general methods that all the EARMARK items have to implement.
EARMARKNode This interface defines all the methods that an EARMARK node have to implement.
EARMARKOntologyURI This interface defines the URI for each ontology used.
EARMARKPropertyURI This interface defines the URI for each EARMARK property.
 

Class Summary
Attribute This class represents a concrete attribute in the EARMARK model.
Bag This class represents a bag, i.e., a non-ordered collection that allows repetitions.
Comment This class represents a concrete comment in the EARMARK model.
Docuverse This class represents an abstract docuverse in the EARMARK model.
EARMARKDocument This class represents an EARMARK document.
Element This class represents a concrete element in the EARMARK model.
List  
MarkupItem This class represents an abstract markup item in the EARMARK model.
PointerRange This class represents a concrete pointer range in the EARMARK model.
Range This class represents a abstract range in the EARMARK model.
Set This class represents a set, i.e., a non-ordered collection that does not allow repetitions.
StringDocuverse This class represents a concrete string docuverse in the EARMARK model.
URIDocuverse This class represents a concrete URI docuverse in the EARMARK model.
XPathPointerRange This class represents an concrete xpath pointer range in the EARMARK model.
XPathRange This class represents an abstract xpath range in the EARMARK model.
 

Enum Summary
Collection.Type An enumeration of all the possible kinds of collections that relates to EARMARK markup items
Docuverse.Type This enumeration describes all the possible types for docuverses.
EARMARKNode.Type An enumeration of all the kinds of EARMARK node.
